            <tr>
               <td class="events"><a class="anchor" id="top" name="concert"></a>
                <h3>Concert including Carmina Burana and other items at the Fairfield Halls. Saturday 2nd April</h3>
                <p>Croydon Philharmonic Choir with Basingstoke choral society and the choir of St Mary's C of E School, Oxted with Docklands Sinfonia present Carmina Burana at The Fairfield Halls on Saturday 2nd April at 7.30pm. Tickets via <%= link_to "Fairfield.co.uk", "https://www.fairfield.co.uk" %>. (Transaction fee applies). Ticket prices £15, £18, £25 and £39.</p>
                <p>Other items include "Rhapsody in Blue" by George Gershwin, and "The Rio Grand" by Lambert</p>
              </td>
                <td class="events">
                  <h3>Fairfield Halls</h3>
              </td>
            </tr>

             <tr>
               <td class="events"><a class="anchor" id="top" name="kingsmead"></a>
                <h3>Open Day at Kingsmead Equestrian Centre. Monday 18th April</h3>
                <p>Kingsmead Equestrian Centre would like to invite you to an Open Day, on Easter Monday, 18th April from 12 noon - 3pm. There will be a variety of workshops and ridden demonstrations, a real life Buckaroo game, as well as a parade featuring our amazing horses and ponies.</p>
                <p>Free pony rides!</p>
                <p>Kingswood Lane, Warlingham, CR0 9AB. 0208 657 0832. <%= link_to "www.kingsmeadhorses.co.uk", "https://www.kingsmeadhorses.co.uk" %></p>
                <p><%= link_to "More information", "resource/Kingsmead_equestrian.pdf" %></p>
              </td>
                <td class="events">
                  <h3><%= link_to "Kingsmead", "https://www.kingsmeadhorses.co.uk" %></h3>
              </td>
            </tr>

