                <p>The SRA AGM will be held on Thursday 12 May 2022 at 7.30 pm in All Saints' large hall, Onslow Gardens, CR2 9AB. All residents are encouraged to attend and members are entitled to vote at the meeting.</p>
              </td>
                <td class="events"><%= link_to image_tag("small-images/residents_logo100.jpg", alt: "SRA logo"), "http://www.sanderstead-residents.co.uk" %>
