                <p>Come and meet new friends and enjoy chatter with fresh home-made cakes and Tea or Coffee, and have fun. Why Not Come and Join us at All Saints' Church Sanderstead in the Small Hall. Fortnightly on Fridays between 10am and 12pm. You will all be made very welcome! Coffee Pot returns on Friday 28 January 2022.</p>
