              <td class="events"><a class="anchor" id="top" name="select"></a>
                <h3>Sanderstead library is now open on Wednesdays, Fridays and Saturdays from 10am - 1pm and from 2pm - 5pm.</h3>
                <p>Sanderstead Library is now operating a Select and Collect service. Books can be reserved online, by email or by phone. You’ll be notified once your items are ready for collection. Please knock on the door when you arrive for your collection and a member of staff will come and help you. For more information and service updates please visit our website: <%= link_to "www.croydon.gov.uk/libraries-leisure-and-culture/libraries/find-your-library/sanderstead-library", "https://www.croydon.gov.uk/libraries-leisure-and-culture/libraries/find-your-library/sanderstead-library" %></p>
