                <p>Meetings commence at 10.30 on the fourth Tuesday of the month at the United Reformed Church Hall, Sanderstead Hill, South Croydon, CR2 0HB.  Coffee is served from 9.45 to 10.15am.</p>
                <p>At present there is no waiting list for new members joining and visitors are welcome on payment of a small fee. For more information phone 0208 660 9122. Email:  suedavenport72@gmail.com</p>
                <p>Meetings are currently held via Zoom. Visit our website for details. <%= link_to "theartssocietysanderstead.org.uk", "https://theartssocietysanderstead.org.uk/AboutUs/AboutUs.aspx" %>
